One shoud insert a udev rule, such that each device always uses the same seria port and such that the user has the rights to read an write to this port. 
like this:
in /etc/udev/rules.d

# HAMEG 4040 MOXA
SUBSYSTEM=="tty", ATTRS{idVendor}=="0403", ATTRS{idProduct}=="ed72", MODE="666", GROUP="group", SYMLINK+="Hameg4040"
SUBSYSTEM=="tty", ATTRS{idVendor}=="06cd", ATTRS{idProduct}=="0121", MODE="666", GROUP="group", SYMLINK+="Keithley"